## Migration Type Support Matrix

| Provider | Cold | Warm | Live | Conversion |
|----------|------|------|------|------------|
| vSphere | Yes | Yes (CBT) | No | Yes |
| oVirt | Yes | Yes (snapshots) | No | Yes |
| OpenStack | Yes | No | No | No |
| OVA | Yes | No | No | No |
| Hyper-V | Yes | No | No | No |
| OpenShift | Yes | No | Yes | Yes |
